## Stimulus Controllers

**File naming:**
- **snake_case, ends with `_controller.js`**: `dropdown_controller.js`, `modal_controller.js`

**HTML identifier:**
- **kebab-case**: `data-controller="dropdown"`, `data-controller="modal"`

```javascript
// Good
// File: app/javascript/controllers/dropdown_controller.js
import { Controller } from "@hotwired/stimulus"

export default class extends Controller {
  // ...
}
```

```html
<!-- HTML usage -->
<div data-controller="dropdown">
  <!-- kebab-case in HTML -->
</div>
```
